videos.description: Dennis Smith Jr. throws up the lob for Abdul-Malik Abu who finishes with authority
videos.headline: Abu catches the alley-oop and throws it down

videos.description: John Gillon finds Tyler Lydon with a perfect bounce pass for the dunk.
videos.headline: Tyler Lydon throws it down in transition

videos.description: For the second time tonight, Dennis Smith Jr. finds Abdul-Malik Abu for the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Abu throws down another alley-oop

videos.description: Dennis Smith Jr. finds BeeJay Anya with a pretty bounce pass for the dunk for NC State
videos.headline: BeeJay Anya dunks it down for NC State

videos.description: Abdul-Malik Abu finds Omer Yurtseven under the basket for the dunk.
videos.headline: NC State opens the half with a dunk from Yurtseven

videos.description: Maverick Rowan buries the 3-pointer off the dish from Dennis Smith Jr.
videos.headline: Maverick Rowan knocks down the 3 to give NC State the lead

videos.description: Omer Yurtseven pins shot to backboard, leading to a Abdul-Malik Abu dunk.
videos.headline: Yurtseven block leads to Abu dunk on the other end

videos.description: Omer Yurtseven assists on Abdul-Malik Abu dunk after getting hit with the ball.
videos.headline: Yurtseven gets hit with ball, gets assist

videos.description: Dennis Smith Jr. kisses the layup  high off the glass and gets it to go.
videos.headline: Dennis Smith Jr.  converts a beautiful reverse layup

videos.description: John Gillon buries his 8th 3-pointer of the night to cap a 12-0 run for the Orange.
videos.headline: John Gillon buries a three to cap a 12-0 run for the Orange

videos.description: Dennis Smith Jr. converts the tip-in to complete for his second triple-double of the season.
videos.headline: Smith gets the tip shot to complete the triple-double

videos.description: Maverick Rowan hits a big time 3-pointer and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Rowan buries a 3 and draws the foul

videos.description: John Gillon's 43-point night powers Syracuse past NC State 100-93 in OT
videos.headline: John Gillon's 43-point night powers Syracuse past NC State 100-93 in OT
